br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最后第三次在台阶上，希美说“请等我一下”。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n自然而然。<br />\r\n","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"1063","username":"堆雪若叶","adminid":"0","groupid":"49","memberstatus":"0","number":"1062","dbdateline":"1544204128","groupiconid":"9"},{"pid":"41870120","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"Bani82","authorid":"105209","dateline":"2018-12-8 01:38","message":"关键其实这两个完全找不到有什么分开的理由啊，不是一个大学就会分开这理论太奇怪了<br />\r\n音乐家的朋友一定是音乐家么？至于两人差距越来越大...这个怎么说呢，可能有影响也可能完全没影响吧<br />\r\n总之找不到一定要分开的理由","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"1064","username":"Bani82","adminid":"0","groupid":"54","memberstatus":"0","number":"1063","dbdateline":"1544204335","groupiconid":"13"},{"pid":"41870134","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"adonai","authorid":"155630","dateline":"2018-12-8 01:41","message":"谁来解释一下，在第二季开始，霙听到希美的笛声说“我讨厌这个声音，想吐”，当时的心态是什么样的？当时霙是怎么想希美的？","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"1065","username":"adonai","adminid":"0","groupid":"52","memberstatus":"0","number":"1064","dbdateline":"1544204470","groupiconid":"10"},{"pid":"41870140","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"Bani82","authorid":"105209","dateline":"2018-12-8 01:42","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=41870134&amp;ptid=1795203\"><font color=\"#999999\">adonai 发表于 2018-12-8 01:41</font></a><br />\r\n谁来解释一下，在第二季开始，霙听到希美的笛声说“我讨厌这个声音，想吐”，当时的心态是什么样的？当时霙 ...</div><br />\n心理阴影，觉得自己被抛弃了","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"1066","username":"Bani82","adminid":"0","groupid":"54","memberstatus":"0","number":"1065","dbdateline":"1544204559","groupiconid":"13"},{"pid":"41870143","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"Chien","authorid":"494568","dateline":"2018-12-8 01:42","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><font color=\"#999999\">Archlich 发表于 2018-12-8 01:31</font><br />\r\n<f